Rhabdoblatta nigrovittata
Bey-Bienko, 1954: 21; 
Princis 1967
: 664; Feng, Guo et Wu 1997: 90; 
Anisyutkin 2003
: 550.

Female slightly different from male and larger. Body pale yellow. Vertex and frons yellowish brown. Stripes on the sterna same as male (Figure 9
A-D
).
